 \Big|\int_1^\sqrt{3} \! \frac{\sin(x)}{e^x(x^2 +1)} \, \mathrm{d} x \Big| \leq \frac{\pi}{12e}
|\sin(x)|
x
 \Big|\int_1^\sqrt{3} \! \frac{\sin(x)}{e^x(x^2 +1)} \, \mathrm{d} x \Big| \leq \int_1^\sqrt{3} \! \frac{|\sin(x)|}{e^x(x^2 +1)} \, \mathrm{d} x \leq \int_1^\sqrt{3} \! \frac{1}{e^x(x^2 +1)} \, \mathrm{d} x
 1<x<\sqrt{3} \implies e<e^x<e^{\sqrt{3}}
|sin(x)|\leq 1
\Big|\int_1^\sqrt{3} \! \frac{\sin(x)}{e^x(x^2 +1)} \, \mathrm{d} x \Big|\leq \int_1^\sqrt{3} \! \frac{1}{e(x^2 +1)} \, \mathrm{d} x  \leq \frac{\pi}{12e}
